asset.author: Victorinox AG
asset.hookText: Werks Traveler 5.0 is more than just luggage. It is a place for your belongings. The things you need, the things you like and the things that help you be you. Why leave any of it behind? Werks Traveler 5.0 has been strategically engineered to weigh less, contain greater capacity and pro-vide more packing options as a result of the intelligent Pack More System. Inspired by the ingenuity and multi-functionality of the Original Swiss Army Knife, the Pack More System includes five different packing solutions.  Pack it your way and travel with more of the things that are important to you.
